  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nTimestamps of messages do not correspond to their real order when messages are fetching from offline.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTimestamps of messages are the same as for the sender\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe order of messages is right, but timestamps are mixing up\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/172573241-50e12340-4c06-4c8f-ad94-a8ac48e85a44.mp4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Device 1: start chat with Device2\r\n2) Device 2: close the app\r\n3) Device 1: send 50 messages in 10 mins\r\n4) Device 2: open the app \r\n5) Device 2: check messages order and timestamps on each of them\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status Version: nightly 08/06/2022\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
