    "body": "This is due to re-transmission, we use the whisper timestamp, which is the time the message is sent, in case of re-transmission it would be more recent.\r\nThe other option is to use a user-defined timestamp, the issue is that is fully controlled by the other client, unfortunately there's no bullet proof solution.",
